rows.label: qst103316_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, wow! Looks like you
didn't need my help.

rows.label: qst103316_msg0002
rows.name: Ughh... I beg you, spare me my life...

rows.label: qst103316_msg0004
rows.name:
I only gave them the details
of milady's routine! I had
no idea they'd...

rows.label: qst103316_msg0005
rows.name: Oh, yes! I have something for you!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0006
rows.name:
It's a key to these
scoundrels' secret hideout!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0007
rows.name:
They're holed up in an old
warehouse in the lower city.

rows.label: qst103316_msg0008
rows.name:
It's true, I swear it!
I wouldn't lie to you!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0009
rows.name:
S-see, I'll provide you
valuable information! I'm
no ally of theirs! So please!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0122
rows.name:
You may not be one of them,
but you'd still better tell
us everything you know!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0151
rows.name:
Please! I had no idea they would kill
milady! You have to believe me!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0152
rows.name:
You can furnish us with the
rest of your lies back at HQ!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0181
rows.name: I'll take this miscreant into custody.

rows.label: qst103316_msg0182
rows.name:
Can I ask you to check
out this secret hideout?

rows.label: qst103316_msg0183
rows.name:
Once I've handed him over
to HQ, I'll go join you.
